567
0:31:55,753 --> 0:31:57,592
Why the fuck not?


568
0:31:57,592 --> 0:32:6,392
Because I love ya.


569
0:32:6,392 --> 0:32:15,312
I love ya!


570
0:32:15,312 --> 0:32:16,712
