to have a serious conversation.


597
0:34:27,712 --> 0:34:28,752
Eric.


598
0:34:28,752 --> 0:34:31,792
Eric.


599
0:34:31,792 --> 0:34:33,192
Eric.


600
0:34:33,192 --> 0:34:38,672
Some folk respond well
to kindness, a soft touch.


601
