614
0:35:11,952 --> 0:35:14,712
That euphoria.


615
0:35:14,712 --> 0:35:16,392
Him.


616
0:35:16,392 --> 0:35:17,273
His need.


617
0:35:17,273 --> 0:35:20,872
My need.


618
0:35:20,872 --> 0:35:23,752
