649
0:37:30,672 --> 0:37:41,672
You know, rattle his tambourine.


650
0:37:41,672 --> 0:37:43,72
Fuck me.


651
0:37:43,72 --> 0:38:13,152
The ice maiden melteth.


652
0:38:13,152 --> 0:38:15,72
