653
0:38:15,72 --> 0:38:16,353
Mostly of regret.


654
0:38:16,353 --> 0:38:19,192
You treated her like shite.


655
0:38:19,192 --> 0:38:21,472
Regret that I ever met her,


656
0:38:21,472 --> 0:38:24,392
