we left off,


657
0:38:24,392 --> 0:38:27,672
cos truth be told, there was nothing
left to pick up.


658
0:38:27,672 --> 0:38:30,472
But, I got me tea made.
Me washing done...


659
0:38:30,472 --> 0:38:32,112
A good nosh now and again.


660
0:38:32,112 --> 0:38:35,112
You bastard!


661
0:38:35,112 --> 0:38:39,152
