now before us?


670
0:39:14,512 --> 0:39:17,472
Much like yourself,
I lived a selfish life,


671
0:39:17,472 --> 0:39:22,152
attending to my needs before even
considering the needs of others.


672
0:39:22,152 --> 0:39:25,872
And then I went back to Ireland
and, while there,


673
0:39:25,872 --> 0:39:31,512
