as my Road To Damascus experience.


674
0:39:31,512 --> 0:39:35,72
Oh, so God just popped up and
showed you the error of your ways?


675
0:39:35,72 --> 0:39:37,112
Yeah? Well, I don't believe a word.


676
0:39:37,112 --> 0:39:40,392
