of them!


732
0:43:59,632 --> 0:44:1,552
I want to be amongst folk I know.


733
0:44:1,552 --> 0:44:4,312
Familiar faces, surroundings.


734
0:44:4,312 --> 0:44:5,992
I want to come home.


735
0:44:5,992 --> 0:44:24,712
And I wanted to make your life
a feckin' misery, Frank.


736
0:44:24,712 --> 0:44:28,272
'I ran into that old boyfriend
a few years ago.


737
0:44:28,272 --> 0:44:30,32
