741
0:44:38,713 --> 0:44:40,272
'All the pain he'd caused.'


742
0:44:40,272 --> 0:44:41,273
Oh, they're here!


743
0:44:41,273 --> 0:44:43,352
'And, if I believed in God,


744
0:44:43,352 --> 0:44:47,592
'I'd like to think he'd had every
sin that he'd ever committed


745
0:44:47,592 --> 0:44:51,552
'scratched into his face
as a warning to others


746
0:44:51,552 --> 0:44:59,72
'to keep their distance - to beware.


747
0:44:59,72 --> 0:45:1,672
'That's if I believed in God.'


748
0:45:1,672 --> 0:45:4,432
What are you going on about?
